# harvest CLI — environment configuration template.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local` for per-machine overrides) and
# fill in real values. Both filenames are gitignored.
#
# Precedence (last wins, but shell vars are NEVER overridden):
#   1. Variables exported in the shell  (highest)
#   2. .env.local
#   3. .env                              (lowest)
#
# Loaded by src/cli/env.ts at the top of `main()`.

# ─── LLM provider selection (PLAN_MULTI_PROVIDER §6) ─────────────────────────

# Active LLM provider. One of: anthropic | openai | google.
# Default: anthropic. The CLI's --provider flag wins over this.
# HARVEST_PROVIDER=anthropic

# ─── Provider API keys (set the one matching HARVEST_PROVIDER) ───────────────

# Required when HARVEST_PROVIDER=anthropic (default). Get one at
# https://console.anthropic.com/. Never commit this value.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Required when HARVEST_PROVIDER=openai. Get one at
# https://platform.openai.com/api-keys.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Required when HARVEST_PROVIDER=google (Gemini). Get one at
# https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey.
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=

# ─── Model selection ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Override the default agent model. Default per provider:
#   anthropic → claude-sonnet-4-6
#   openai    → gpt-4.1
#   google    → gemini-2.5-pro
# The CLI's --model flag wins over this.
# HARVEST_MODEL=

# Override the EXTRACT-step model used by the extract_items_from_transcript
# tool. Default: HARVEST_MODEL → provider default.
# HARVEST_EXTRACT_MODEL=

# ─── Test / replay knobs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Switch the LLM caller. One of: live | mock | replay | record.
# Default: live. Most tests run under replay or mock.
# HARVEST_TEST_LLM=live

# ─── Discovery ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Override the transcript-search root. Default: ~/.claude/projects.
# HARVEST_TRANSCRIPT_DIR=

# ─── Debug ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Set to 1 to dump raw LLM I/O on stderr (also enables .env load summary).
# HARVEST_DEBUG=
